{"tid":34612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先有MK仔想同我隻挑隻!!","createTime":"2016-12-11T14:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T11:52:21.000Z","uid":14191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"425b435a6bcc6fb7f9b42d489263e8f984a51ffe","tid":34612,"uid":14191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:38:10.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學 <br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪 <br />\n<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打 <br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉 <br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型 <br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎) <br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿 <br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」 <br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」 <br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲 <br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量 <br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過 <br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間 <br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇 <br />\n佢就除左件校服 <br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔 <br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋 <br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"efc98eb5c6802018b41181f912a186cd669cc24b","tid":34612,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:39:07.000Z","msg":"又回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4de075a075ee14fb1e85e9a27dc5d75fa4cdba4","tid":34612,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:39:33.000Z","msg":"又頭先又想當年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da54bd9f37c0fd5d19d4162b050790d9ea921ec7","tid":34612,"uid":14191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cf29fac87b1b148a473d05fc25567433c7978b","tid":34612,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img s